videos.description: Shamorie Ponds hangs and gets the floater to go for St. John's.
videos.headline: Ponds knocks down baseline floater

videos.description: Jagan Mosely rocks the rim after making a great cut for Georgetown.
videos.headline: Mosely clears the lane for huge slam

videos.description: Justin Simon and Tariq Owens throw a pair of alley-oops down for St. Johns on back-to-back possessions.
videos.headline: Simon and Owens try and break MSG rims with alley-oops

videos.description: Justin Simon takes it hard to the rack and gets the foul to go along with the bucket for St. Johns.
videos.headline: Simon puts the Red Storm ahead with and-1

videos.description: Justin Simon picks up the rebound after Tariq Owens' block and scores on the other end for the Red Storm.
videos.headline: Simon turns good defense into offense
